{"id": 3025, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常中你都是如何扮演一个“社懒”选手的？", "description": "社交懒惰，一种“并不社恐，但也不会积极社交”的状态，简称社懒。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 12644, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191008214856aDWCvOnNrw8VKJLS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-08T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5960, "title": "日常中你都是如何扮演一个“社懒”选手的？", "content": "日常中你都是如何扮演一个“社懒”选手的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348036, "content": "聚餐时不主动抛出话题，但有人 cue 自己也不会闷着", "image": "img/option/option/20191008201731bLhxflDRQEkPH0y4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348037, "content": "出门自带耳机结界，但跟人说话时都一定会摘下耳机", "image": "img/option/option/201910082020203CPoU1YTHjcmkGMX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348038, "content": "对他人的求助很热情，与此同时却很少主动找人寒暄", "image": "img/option/option/20191008202707Hzp78guRAhYqD1Cc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348043, "content": "不常发朋友圈/微博，但遇到喜欢的话题就会多发几条", "image": "img/option/option/20191008204711l9QJResvcy0qEbdS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348044, "content": "聊天时比较随性，有话题就多聊点，没有也不会尬聊", "image": "img/option/option/20191008205556VnYMxwc410DgilbU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348045, "content": "会在意社交中的措辞，但不会为自己的表现耿耿于怀", "image": "img/option/option/20191008205818WOX7nGcLglxv5M3T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348046, "content": "习惯性友好，不会因为对方的身份而刻意热情/冷淡", "image": "img/option/option/20191008210504XeVSvqHtQ4sRExu9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348047, "content": "觉得一个人更自在，但也不会刻意拒绝社交场合", "image": "img/option/option/20191008210727VFgrWjvKG4YPCshD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348048, "content": "咦，我好像都没有", "image": "img/option/option/20191008211305H2R3wfkeDKg6M1sG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}